sentences.english: Because of her strange clothing, she didn’t fit in well with the rest of the students.

sentences.english: He and his father are two, I hear.

sentences.english: I can hardly imagine two men less capable of getting on together.
sentences.chinese: 很難想象有比他們倆在一起更合不來的人。

sentences.english: " Pride and poverty don't get along, but often live together. " —Proverb.
